### POST /api/v1/admin/tariffs/{id}/activate
### Descripción: Activar plan de tarifa. Requiere Admin/Support + X-Tenant-Id.
### Headers requeridos: Authorization: Bearer <token>, X-Tenant-Id: <guid>
### Códigos: 200 OK (TariffPlanDto) | 404 | 403 | 400 (TARIFF_PRIORITY_CONFLICT, etc.)

# @name activateTariff
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/admin/tariffs/{{TARIFF_ID}}/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{ACCESS_TOKEN}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{TENANT_ID}}

### Response esperado (200): TariffPlanDto
### Response error (404): TARIFF_NOT_FOUND
### Response error (400): TARIFF_PRIORITY_CONFLICT u otros
